# vim: syn=perl

=head1 NAME

_POL2_HELLO_ - POL-2 introductory primitive

=head1 SYNOPSIS

_POL2_HELLO_

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This primitive should be called at the start of all POL-2 recipes.

=head1 NOTES

Currently this primitive simply checks that POL-2 is in the beam.

